0.3.0 2023-02-03

    - Check OpenAPI version.
    - Accept raw JSON in new().
    - Make a copy of input value to new() in order not to overwrite it.
    - Make unexposed methods private.
    - Add methods api() and parameters().
    - Skip adding JavaScript if no 'path' placeholders need replacing.
    - Add POD.

0.2.0 2022-10-21

    - Follow OpenAPI guidelines for prefixing custom properties.
    - Mark mandatory fields as required in HTML forms.
    - Drop URL parameter format from tables in RST format.
    - Autogenerating META.json.

0.1.0 2020-01-31

    - Initial release.
